65!

15
00:02:43,250 --> 00:02:44,350
70!

16
00:02:44,350 --> 00:02:45,350
75!

17
00:02:49,850 --> 00:02:51,250
80!

18
00:02:51,250 --> 00:02:52,750
85!

19
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:53,960
100 milionů.

20
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:56,800
Máme tu nabídku 100 miliónů.

21
00:02:56,800 --> 00:03:00,430
